OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,FThursday evening and overnight with
OL,7,Ffurther patchy rain and drizzle,
OL,8,Fespecially over the hills. A band of
OL,9,Fheavier rain then arriving into
OL,10,FCornwall near dawn. South or
OL,11,Fsouthwesterly winds gradually
OL,12,Fincreasing, becoming blustery along
OL,13,Fcoasts.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FA cloudy start with a band of
OL,16,Frain gradually spreading eastward,
OL,17,Freaching far eastern parts by evening.
OL,18,FTurning drier and brighter from the
OL,19,Fwest later, with winds gradually
OL,20,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
