OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Flargely fine and dry weekend as high
OL,7,Fpressure builds in. Feeling pleasant
OL,8,Fin any sunshine with lighter winds.
OL,9,FLikely to remain similar early next
OL,10,Fweek as high pressure dominates.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
